data.description: MLS# 270819 Escape to the tranquility of the countryside and embrace a peaceful and picturesque lifestyle in this charming home located in Pasco. Nestled on a sprawling 5-acre lot, this property offers breathtaking scenery and ample space for your animals to roam. Step inside the 1809 sq ft manufactured home and you'll be greeted by a spacious living area with vaulted ceilings, creating an open and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen offers plenty of counter and cabinet space to accommodate all your needs and just off the kitchen, you'll find a large dining area, perfect for hosting meals and gatherings with loved ones. This home features four generously sized bedrooms and 2 full baths, providing ample space for everyone. The primary suite with an extra large closet, a dual sink vanity, a soaking tub, and a separate shower, offers a private retreat for relaxation. Outside, immerse yourself in the joys of country living. The 5 acres of land offer endless possibilities, with a chicken coop and corrals for your animals. The property also boasts a delightful fruit orchard, allowing you to indulge in the harvest of nature's bounty.Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to experience the serenity and beauty of country living. Contact us now to schedule a showing and make this peaceful retreat your own.
